  {
    "path": "/changelog/2026-06-04-team-documents",
    "url": "https://linear.app/changelog/2026-06-04-team-documents",
    "label": "Team documentsImportant team context doesn’t always belong in a specific issue, project, or initiative. Teams also need a dedicated place for the notes, docs, and shared references that support their work over time. Now, every team has a page to keep its context organized and easy to access.Jun 3, 2026",
    "area": "body"
  },
  {
    "path": "/changelog/2026-06-11-coding-sessions",
    "url": "https://linear.app/changelog/2026-06-11-coding-sessions",
    "label": "Coding sessions in LinearEarlier this year, we launched Linear Agent, giving teams a new way to plan and coordinate their issues and projects. Since then, we've added Code Intelligence to extend that understanding to the codebase, and MCP support to bring all of your context together.Jun 10, 2026",
    "area": "body"
  },
  {
    "path": "/changelog/2026-06-18-agent-assisted-project-updates",
    "url": "https://linear.app/changelog/2026-06-18-agent-assisted-project-updates",
    "label": "Agent assisted project updatesProject and initiative updates keep teams aligned, but writing them means pulling out recent changes from issues, documents, and discussions.Jun 17, 2026",
    "area": "body"
  },
  {
    "path": "/changelog/2026-07-02-initiative-properties",
